TITLE: Implementing Optimistic Cart Updates in React
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to use the new useOptimisticCart() hook to apply optimistic updates to the cart, improving perceived performance when adding or modifying items.
SOURCE: https://github.com/Shopify/hydrogen/blob/main/packages/hydrogen/CHANGELOG.md#2025-04-11_snippet_8

LANGUAGE: tsx
CODE:
```
export function Cart({cart}) {
  const optimisticCart = useOptimisticCart(cart);

  if (!optimisticCart?.lines?.nodes?.length) return <p>Nothing in cart</p>;

  return optimisticCart.lines.nodes.map((line) => (
